### Add product to favorites
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/{{productId}}/favorite
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Remove product from favorites
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/{{productId}}/favorite
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get favorite products (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get favorite products (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/favorites?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
